{
  "stem": "2316.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, she has to concentrate 24 hours, till she gets her signals, so she can read somebody else's fortune.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how we got food traveling on the trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was telling their fortunes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way, my father-- the train stopped someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father had to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went to urinate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, he missed the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It took a month for my father to find us again, because we took so many trains to get there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, we were-- we were heading already to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were traveling on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it only went so far, because the tracks were broken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if we want to take another train, you're [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have to-- you're gonna have to wait here 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on track number three, there might be a cattle train, or some train that might take us farther.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know where it came from and who had it, but there was a mattress, or inner spring, or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We put it across the tracks, and seven people are lying down on the mattress to sleep a little bit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the train comes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It throws the mattress off the tracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nobody got killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My mother flew, maybe-- I don't know how many feet threw her high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everybody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were-- what happened is they hit the mattress, and the mattress kept flying with the people on it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This one fell here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This-- my mother was injured the most.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All of us got very injured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody got killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Another miracle.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And from there, we got-- and the feathers started to fly and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And from there, we gathered again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We're waiting for-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We walked on foot someplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
